name: Apphance-Production
summary: Apphance SDK meant for production releases.
description: uTest Apphance is a set of tools that closes the feedback loop between app creators, testers and users to help ensure the best app quality possible. With uTest Apphance you can stay on top of your app's quality in the lab and in production.
